In [[Calimshan]], Yogurt was used to served minced [[pigeon]] hearts in [[lamb]]s' bones.

[[Goat]]'s milk yogurt was a common type of produce in various lands of [[Zakhara]], including [[Jumlat]] and the [[Pearl Cities]].

In the secluded [[Malatran Plateau]], some chefs of the [[Saiyama]] tribe served succulent roasted goat rubbed with [[sage (herb)|sage]], roasted tubers, and goat's milk yogurt.{{Cite living jungle/Recipe for Disaster|16}}
